      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "I'LLTELLYOUTONIGHT (4) will appreciate the step back in grade after finishing fifth last start over 1350m at Doomben, that effort coming on the back of a win two back at Gold Coast. Can do much better in this more suitable race. MISTER MIGHTY (3) kicked off this campaign with a win two runs ago. Less impressive last time out when fourth over 1200m at Toowoomba, beaten 3.5 lengths. Looks well placed so expect a better run this time. GLAMOUR MAN (2) is a three-year-old gelding who is having his first run for the Todd Pollard stable. Scored at his latest appearance at Wangaratta six months ago. Ran sixth in a trial at Deagon over 1050m and looks well placed. Should feature in the finish. I'M NELSON (5) best of the rest.",
